# Exploring Data Types

<img src="https://images.code.org/be59c99d32b20fa2098483c9963e3114-image-1741196021063.png" alt="house with a garden and a tree" width="125px" style="border-radius:10px; float:left; margin: 0 20px 0px 0px;">

#### Imagine you are the local community center organizer.
#### You have received a set of data cards representing different types of neighborhood information: house numbers, resident names, street names, home prices, and whether a house has a garden. 
#### **Your task?** Sort these cards and notice patterns in the data.

<div style="clear:both;"></div>

---
